section#aboutInfriendsProgram.about-us
  .container
    .section-header
      h2.white-text  Infriends Program
      p.white-text.shortDescription
        | We contribute to understanding, friendship and cooperation among students.
    .row
      .col-lg-4.col-md-4.column
        .big-intro.wow.fadeInLeft.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
          | We are students who want to help you!
      .col-lg-8.col-md-8.column
        .wow.fadeInUp.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
          p.white-text
          | This program is driven by FIUBA International Network, which is made up entirely of
          | FIUBA students and seeks to increase the interaction between local and foreign students
          | and, achieving the full potential of intercultural experiences from student exchanges.
          |<br/><br/> The aim of InFriends is to promote personal development and student mobility
          | based on the principle of students helping students and internationalization at home.
    .our-clients
      p
        span.section-footer-title AN INFRIEND WILL BE ASIGNED TO YOU
    .row
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-3.focus-box.red.wow.fadeInLeft.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
        .service-icon
          i.pixeden.pd-icon-email-marketing
        h3.red-border-bottom Contact you
        p
          | Your InFriend will contact you by email a couple of weeks before the semester starts.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-3.focus-box.green.wow.fadeInLeft.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
        .service-icon
          i.pixeden.pd-icon-map
        h3.green-border-bottom Arrival
        p
          | Your InFriend will pick you up at the airport.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-3.focus-box.blue.wow.fadeInRight.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
        .service-icon
          i.pixeden.pd-icon-truck
        h3.blue-border-bottom Means of transport
        p
          | Your InFriend will help you with the several means of transport of the city.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-3.focus-box.yellow.wow.fadeInRight.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
        .service-icon
          i.pixeden.pd-icon-tablet
        h3.yellow-border-bottom Help you
        p
          | Your InFriend will help you with the courses which you want to take.

section#activities.works
  .container
    .section-header
      h2.dark-text Activities
      p.shortDescription
        | We organize several kinds of activites.
    .row.projects
      #loader
        .loader-icon
      #portfolio-list.col-md-12
        ul.cbp-rfgrid
          li.wow.fadeInLeft.animated data-wow-delay="0.15s" data-wow-duration="1.5s" data-wow-offset="30"
            a data-ng-click="open(activity.id)"
              img alt="activity" data-ng-src="{{activity.imageUrl}}" src="" /
              .project-info
                .project-details
                  h5.white-text.red-border-bottom  {activity.name}
                  .details.white-text  {activity.details}

